title: [Fragrant Fables]
description: Hemp-latticed walls are engulfed in hand-blown iridescent glass bubbles, the spheres haloing the kelp-draped shelves scattered throughout the shop.  A glitter-covered resaeun nielira dominates the center of the rug-covered floor, the sea creature's elongated arms each displaying a shell-shaped tray filled with a variety of colorful glass bottles.
